The Good : it 's a fun co-op game & SP game ( never tried PvP ) . ||| 1
Huge world with beautiful graphics . ||| 1
Fun and distinctive classes . ||| 1
A lot of humor and interesting quests if you take time to read them . ||| 1
Huge cities within the world . ||| 1
If you liked Diablo and Titan Quest , I have no doubt you 'll like this game . ||| 1
The Bad : As of May 2009 , there are still critical bugs left in the game . ||| 1
Be aware that the game will likely crash for you at some point . ||| 1
Not enough bugs that I would n't recommend to buy it , based on the fact that it works fairly well for me . ||| 1
Bugs are the primary reason I believe this game is n't a solid 9 . ||| 1
